  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/e38f1284032cbc18976f51f5d08de3b0.avif?t=1770062324\" width=615 height=152 /></span><br>Definitive Edition is out now! You can enjoy the full game with all the DLCs included!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/d19a3fc8e187a75593bdeee816fba503.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>Songs for a Hero</strong> Is an OLD-SCHOOL SUNG-THROUGH VIDEOGAME STRAVAGANZA! Join an unlikely hero as he sings his way through a strange world full of floating platforms, bright and colorful enemies, and many other inexplicable phenomena in an adventure unlike anything you have ever heard!<br><br>This humorous old-school platformer features a fully dynamic soundtrack that reacts to your every input, meaning that the hero will always sing and crack jokes about whatever is happening to him, whenever it happens.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >With the Definitive Edition, you have access to all Songs for a Hero DLCs:</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/fb5596f68c82b90759a2a70b04aa761b.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SONGS FOR THE DEAD</strong><br>A spooky chapter for \"Songs for a Hero\". Fight your way through 3 levels with haunted mansions and crypts full of dark creatures that might as well have come straight from a horror movie. A brand-new campaign with plenty of heavy metal and rock'n'roll!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/5a758ca30135b142ffa35523c3830566.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SONGS FOR A HERO: EPILOGUE</strong><br>A campaign that takes place right after the Hero's last mission in Songs for a Hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/3e4db580641cbbe162585756c8d32350.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SAMBA FOR A HERO</strong><br>Nothing better than taking a vacation after tons of adventures, am I right? A new level inspired by the Brazilian Samba and Carnival!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/905dae0158185b8c83b88469eafbb015.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SKIN PACKS</strong><br>Here is your chance to play like a Slime, Snake, Dogs or Cactus. Also, now you can customize your hero with new heads!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/d19a3fc8e187a75593bdeee816fba503.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>Songs for a Hero</strong> Is an OLD-SCHOOL SUNG-THROUGH VIDEOGAME STRAVAGANZA! Join an unlikely hero as he sings his way through a strange world full of floating platforms, bright and colorful enemies, and many other inexplicable phenomena in an adventure unlike anything you have ever heard!<br><br>This humorous old-school platformer features a fully dynamic soundtrack that reacts to your every input, meaning that the hero will always sing and crack jokes about whatever is happening to him, whenever it happens.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >With the Definitive Edition, you have access to all Songs for a Hero DLCs:</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/fb5596f68c82b90759a2a70b04aa761b.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SONGS FOR THE DEAD</strong><br>A spooky chapter for \"Songs for a Hero\". Fight your way through 3 levels with haunted mansions and crypts full of dark creatures that might as well have come straight from a horror movie. A brand-new campaign with plenty of heavy metal and rock'n'roll!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/5a758ca30135b142ffa35523c3830566.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SONGS FOR A HERO: EPILOGUE</strong><br>A campaign that takes place right after the Hero's last mission in Songs for a Hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/3e4db580641cbbe162585756c8d32350.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SAMBA FOR A HERO</strong><br>Nothing better than taking a vacation after tons of adventures, am I right? A new level inspired by the Brazilian Samba and Carnival!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389170/extras/905dae0158185b8c83b88469eafbb015.avif?t=1770062324\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><strong>SKIN PACKS</strong><br>Here is your chance to play like a Slime, Snake, Dogs or Cactus. Also, now you can customize your hero with new heads!",
